sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as odh-model-controller<br/>Webhook 9443/TCP
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>8081/TCP Health
    participant Route as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Service
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant APIServer as model-serving-api<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>50051/TCP gRPC
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NVCR as nvcr.io Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Predictor: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment (Traditional)
        User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / User credential
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission webhook<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / Webhook TLS cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit (validated)
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route, ServiceMonitor,<br/>Metrics Service, KEDA TriggerAuth<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / SA token
        Note over Controller: Sub-reconcilers:<br/>Route, Metrics, SM,<br/>Dashboard, CRB, KEDA
        User->>Route: Inference request<br/>HTTPS TLS Edge/Reencrypt
        Route->>Predictor: Forward<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        Predictor-->>Route: Prediction response
        Route-->>User: Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over User,Authorino: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService Deployment (Gateway API)
        User->>K8sAPI: POST LLMInferenceService<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / User credential
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (Kuadrant)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / SA token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter (Istio)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / SA token
        User->>Gateway: Inference request<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / Bearer token
        Gateway->>Authorino: Auth check (via EnvoyFilter)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 TLS service-ca.crt / mTLS
        Authorino->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SAR<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Auth decision
        Authorino-->>Gateway: Allow/Deny
        Gateway->>Predictor: Forward (post-auth)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        Predictor-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>User: Response
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,NVCR: Flow 3: NIM Account Lifecycle
        User->>K8sAPI: POST NIM Account<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / User credential
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Singleton validation<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event
        Controller->>NGC: Validate API key<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / Bearer token
        NGC-->>Controller: Key valid
        Controller->>NGC: Fetch runtime catalog<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / Bearer token
        NGC-->>Controller: Runtime catalog
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create pull Secret,<br/>ConfigMap, OCP Templates<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / SA token
        Note over NVCR: KServe uses pull secret<br/>for nvcr.io image pull
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Dashboard,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Gateway Discovery (Dashboard)
        Dashboard->>APIServer: GET /api/v1/gateways<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / Bearer token (user)
        APIServer->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / Bearer token passthrough
        K8sAPI-->>APIServer: Access granted
        APIServer->>K8sAPI: List Gateways<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / SA token
        K8sAPI-->>APIServer: Gateway list
        APIServer-->>Dashboard: Filtered gateways<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    end
